# Cursor Rules

Read [AGENTS.md](AGENTS.md) first. It routes agents to the smaller domain files that keep context focused:

- [ARCHITECTURE.md](ARCHITECTURE.md)
- [TESTING.md](TESTING.md)
- [TYPESCRIPT.md](TYPESCRIPT.md)
- [PYTHON.md](PYTHON.md)
- [BUILD.md](BUILD.md)
- [SKILLS.md](SKILLS.md)

Use pnpm and Turbo for the TypeScript workspace. Use the Docker pytest flow for `apps/api`. Do not edit generated output, dependency directories, or secrets.
